079   /**
080    * Returns <jk>true</jk> if the specified annotation contains all default values.
081    *
082    * @param a The annotation to check.
083    * @return <jk>true</jk> if the specified annotation contains all default values.
084    */
085   public static boolean empty(Schema a) {
086      return a == null || DEFAULT.equals(a);
087   }
088
089   /**
090    * Converts the specified <ja>@Schema</ja> annotation into a generic map.
091    *
092    * @param a The annotation instance.  Can be <jk>null</jk>.
093    * @return The schema converted to a map, or and empty map if the annotation was null.
094    * @throws ParseException Malformed input encountered.
095    */
096   public static JsonMap asMap(Schema a) throws ParseException {
097      if (a == null)
098         return JsonMap.EMPTY_MAP;
099      JsonMap m = new JsonMap();
100      if (SchemaAnnotation.empty(a))
101         return m;
102      Predicate<String> ne = Utils::isNotEmpty;
103      Predicate<Collection<?>> nec = Utils::isNotEmpty;
104      Predicate<Map<?,?>> nem = Utils::isNotEmpty;
105      Predicate<Boolean> nf = Utils::isTrue;
106      Predicate<Long> nm1 = Utils::isNotMinusOne;
107      return m
108         .appendIf(nem, "additionalProperties", parseMap(a.additionalProperties()))
109         .appendIf(ne, "allOf", joinnl(a.allOf()))
110         .appendFirst(ne, "collectionFormat", a.collectionFormat(), a.cf())
111         .appendIf(ne, "default", joinnl(a._default(), a.df()))
112         .appendIf(ne, "discriminator", a.discriminator())
113         .appendIf(ne, "description", joinnl(a.description(), a.d()))
114         .appendFirst(nec, "enum", parseSet(a._enum()), parseSet(a.e()))
115         // Handle exclusiveMaximum with Draft 2020-12 fallback
116         .appendIf(ne, "exclusiveMaximum", 
117            ne.test(a.exclusiveMaximumValue()) ? a.exclusiveMaximumValue() : 
118            (a.exclusiveMaximum() || a.emax()) ? "true" : null)
119         // Handle exclusiveMinimum with Draft 2020-12 fallback
120         .appendIf(ne, "exclusiveMinimum", 
121            ne.test(a.exclusiveMinimumValue()) ? a.exclusiveMinimumValue() : 
122            (a.exclusiveMinimum() || a.emin()) ? "true" : null)
123         .appendIf(nem, "externalDocs", ExternalDocsAnnotation.merge(m.getMap("externalDocs"), a.externalDocs()))
124         .appendFirst(ne, "format", a.format(), a.f())
125         .appendIf(ne, "ignore", a.ignore() ? "true" : null)
126         .appendIf(nem, "items", merge(m.getMap("items"), a.items()))
127         .appendFirst(ne, "maximum", a.maximum(), a.max())
128         .appendFirst(nm1, "maxItems", a.maxItems(), a.maxi())
129         .appendFirst(nm1, "maxLength", a.maxLength(), a.maxl())
130         .appendFirst(nm1, "maxProperties", a.maxProperties(), a.maxp())
131         .appendFirst(ne, "minimum", a.minimum(), a.min())
132         .appendFirst(nm1, "minItems", a.minItems(), a.mini())
133         .appendFirst(nm1, "minLength", a.minLength(), a.minl())
134         .appendFirst(nm1, "minProperties", a.minProperties(), a.minp())
135         .appendFirst(ne, "multipleOf", a.multipleOf(), a.mo())
136         .appendFirst(ne, "pattern", a.pattern(), a.p())
137         .appendIf(nem, "properties", parseMap(a.properties()))
138         .appendIf(nf, "readOnly", a.readOnly() || a.ro())
139         .appendIf(nf, "required", a.required() || a.r())
140         .appendIf(ne, "title", a.title())
141         .appendFirst(ne, "type", a.type(), a.t())
142         .appendIf(nf, "uniqueItems", a.uniqueItems() || a.ui())
143         .appendIf(ne, "xml", joinnl(a.xml()))
144         .appendIf(ne, "$ref", a.$ref())
145         // JSON Schema Draft 2020-12 properties
146         .appendIf(ne, "const", joinnl(a._const()))
147         .appendIf(nec, "examples", a.examples().length == 0 ? null : Arrays.asList(a.examples()))
148         .appendIf(ne, "$comment", joinnl(a.$comment()))
149         .appendIf(nf, "deprecated", a.deprecatedProperty())
150         .appendIf(ne, "contentMediaType", a.contentMediaType())
151         .appendIf(ne, "contentEncoding", a.contentEncoding())
152         .appendIf(ne, "prefixItems", joinnl(a.prefixItems()))
153         .appendIf(ne, "unevaluatedItems", joinnl(a.unevaluatedItems()))
154         .appendIf(ne, "unevaluatedProperties", joinnl(a.unevaluatedProperties()))
155         .appendIf(ne, "dependentSchemas", joinnl(a.dependentSchemas()))
156         .appendIf(ne, "dependentRequired", joinnl(a.dependentRequired()))
157         .appendIf(ne, "if", joinnl(a._if()))
158         .appendIf(ne, "then", joinnl(a._then()))
159         .appendIf(ne, "else", joinnl(a._else()))
160         .appendIf(ne, "$defs", joinnl(a.$defs()))
161         .appendIf(ne, "$id", a.$id())
162      ;
163   }
164
165   private static JsonMap merge(JsonMap m, Items a) throws ParseException {
166      if (ItemsAnnotation.empty(a))
167         return m;
168      Predicate<String> ne = Utils::isNotEmpty;
169      Predicate<Collection<?>> nec = Utils::isNotEmpty;
170      Predicate<Map<?,?>> nem = Utils::isNotEmpty;
171      Predicate<Boolean> nf = Utils::isTrue;
172      Predicate<Long> nm1 = Utils::isNotMinusOne;
173      return m
174         .appendFirst(ne, "collectionFormat", a.collectionFormat(), a.cf())
175         .appendIf(ne, "default", joinnl(a._default(), a.df()))
176         .appendFirst(nec, "enum", parseSet(a._enum()), parseSet(a.e()))
177         .appendFirst(ne, "format", a.format(), a.f())
178         .appendIf(nf, "exclusiveMaximum", a.exclusiveMaximum() || a.emax())
179         .appendIf(nf, "exclusiveMinimum", a.exclusiveMinimum() || a.emin())
180         .appendIf(nem, "items", SubItemsAnnotation.merge(m.getMap("items"), a.items()))
181         .appendFirst(ne, "maximum", a.maximum(), a.max())
182         .appendFirst(nm1, "maxItems", a.maxItems(), a.maxi())
183         .appendFirst(nm1, "maxLength", a.maxLength(), a.maxl())
184         .appendFirst(ne, "minimum", a.minimum(), a.min())
185         .appendFirst(nm1, "minItems", a.minItems(), a.mini())
186         .appendFirst(nm1, "minLength", a.minLength(), a.minl())
187         .appendFirst(ne, "multipleOf", a.multipleOf(), a.mo())
188         .appendFirst(ne, "pattern", a.pattern(), a.p())
189         .appendIf(nf, "uniqueItems", a.uniqueItems() || a.ui())
190         .appendFirst(ne, "type", a.type(), a.t())
191         .appendIf(ne, "$ref", a.$ref())
192      ;
193   }

212      String $ref="", cf="", collectionFormat="", discriminator="", f="", format="", max="", maximum="", min="", minimum="", mo="", multipleOf="", p="", pattern="", t="", title="", type="";
213      String[] _default={}, _enum={}, additionalProperties={}, allOf={}, d={}, description={}, df={}, e={}, properties={}, value={}, xml={};
214      // JSON Schema Draft 2020-12 properties
215      boolean deprecatedProperty;
216      String $id="", contentMediaType="", contentEncoding="", exclusiveMaximumValue="", exclusiveMinimumValue="";

1513
1514   /**
1515    * Applies targeted {@link Schema} annotations to a {@link org.apache.juneau.Context.Builder}.
1516    */
1517   public static class Apply extends AnnotationApplier<Schema,Context.Builder> {
1518
1519      /**
1520       * Constructor.
1521       *
1522       * @param vr The resolver for resolving values in annotations.
1523       */
1524      public Apply(VarResolverSession vr) {
1525         super(Schema.class, Context.Builder.class, vr);
1526      }
1527
1528      @Override
1529      public void apply(AnnotationInfo<Schema> ai, Context.Builder b) {
1530         Schema a = ai.inner();
1531         if (isEmptyArray(a.on(), a.onClass()))
1532            return;
1533         b.annotations(a);
1534      }
1535   }
